<note id="fs-idm254736" class="learning-objectives">
<label/>
<title>Section Learning Objectives</title>
<para id="fs-idp37274960">By the end of this section, you will be able to do the following:</para>
<list id="fs-idp9734704">
<item>Explain the kinematic equations related to acceleration and illustrate them with graphs</item>
<item>Apply the kinematic equations and related graphs to problems involving acceleration</item>
</list>
</note>

<note id="fs-idp13564336" class="os-teacher"><title>Teacher Support</title>
<para id="fs-idp5402128">The Learning Objectives in this section will help your students master the following standards:</para>
