<para id="fs-idp39305744">List the knowns: time <emphasis effect="italics">t</emphasis> = 1.00 s, 2.00 s, and 3.00 s; initial velocity <emphasis effect="italics">v</emphasis><sub>0</sub> = 13 m/s; acceleration <emphasis effect="italics">a</emphasis> = <emphasis effect="italics">g</emphasis> = –9.80 m/s<sup>2</sup>; and position <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis><sub>0</sub> = 0 m</para>
<para id="fs-idp103439792">List the unknowns: <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis><sub>1</sub>, <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis><sub>2</sub>, and <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis><sub>3</sub>; <emphasis effect="italics">v</emphasis><sub>1</sub>, <emphasis effect="italics">v</emphasis><sub>2</sub>, and <emphasis effect="italics">v</emphasis><sub>3</sub>—where 1, 2, 3 refer to times 1.00 s, 2.00 s, and 3.00 s</para>
<para id="fs-idm1373856">Choose the equations.</para>
<equation id="fs-id1164566840202"> <m:math>
 
