<para id="fs-id1164565355060">A student calculated the final velocity of a train that decelerated from 30.5 m/s and got an answer of −43.34 m/s. Which of the following might indicate that he made a mistake in his calculation?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164565490384" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>The sign of the final velocity is wrong.</item>
